Je0C6HbAr1NV9dpug3m1j6MxtSmvWVHQji4dD8/g6S3E7WHIhF3GMw6YM2k8bI9-vX4d6QT/7" target="_blank"&gt;促使公司扩大其美国项目&lt;/a&gt;。卢特尼克（Lutnick）的目标是在不增加联邦赠款规模的情况下产生数百亿美元的额外投资承诺。此举紧随台湾半导体制造业的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/1yPyLkTWT2oZwDbuj5ciYghdSQllAvHnOSHxabhsQ3bhGoIoP8YNIvaA6BJyMXpfrzcGMgrsbxHK0v2TuTR-Lp3uXKso0r3c0t1V5tLwv3YeVAQnhQACRy0BKxtmCB7dFCGFXJTMI0bqICfgkd0Nz4xZ_A9gfsC_pu9zcj1L669x2mQk1aofEgp0fmXMXjXOCsUfzdqoJpBRHCNFvf1Riuo61tabQFTPn_wTI4MoTeeIUyyTyjh-63nV9CHqgJhu1Ls7KnIeQ9TilYYyhKOwuqPrzlKDxDSq2LRaYUrpND8Ha0BPg3vgMU0pVNkmdJD0PbTiOI-FXxX8_ETxwBOTyibCqKiG97mSg9QSea5rN6LbH0n0iv5WLxB6tLA/XIXclYf5KO43HqK9mzsvovt7UyasCGg7/7" target="_blank"&gt;1000亿美元支出承诺&lt;/a&gt;。同时，唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）创建了一个新办公室，以管理《筹码法》的资金并&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/Z6y9VQbR5UF5aXALX9bgFrFx0PSZaIRiiTDqPaE_v1s0xnNYY7M7lI46cXGKTpusM3Y6wP8nkbHFnLCW3e08JWEmDdCcOAL3fGsz4wZnRbQO0BvSpu8h1bOWlM1pqBF7e5jg0aWj7KxsS8CjBQmBYKXy-pEDPCfxu2tqJlXYG3j685vwhnTiZvHqd_bUJv0UDkRpGCR7-5jbYPwlkPtx-rX-NvOQPs35n7NvktkD0iWbAymlUBSnhjIbSRkajp36sdsjGs8xf1XlHcU-Uh8PBaO74bOhouAM6a39bl35t-29KPgIqckepGHD_SnGu4orc-pAp7DADcwnDHT4TDn8G53Lour5pgsj2yF81C1Iywt1mB-vKBDlK0prykY/Hs5BorgWQCN3ljNtDf3L6XCAP46epo6l/7" target="_blank"&gt;加快在美国的投资&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;由于关税将在&lt;/strong&gt;本周生效，因此美国汽车制造商做出了最后的努力，以说服特朗普政府对他们进行调整，并认为对他们在国外提供的数千个部分的征税&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/Q9xglP17yb7zMTMsKkGOkuQV5mDdayBatePfN4OeiOsFDksHM5fMmzwc19qoi8yzU-a3T7-_v99Wv1fUFjJ_LL5yXbL4y0T1G8uHD2Azlo2V9OVgaLVnLjMK1XGJterbAyuwOO5yqa7158NVWKqscUG52fsaPTFnTJhqGHgCZQuo1LUq-q1jKGyABy_oIOttXzmgyN6OtyE-VB2-Hf0sv1y4p2sb-SLnV4ocSi26gnAEGPgsKJkdXj3PwZmZeLa6pkqGwmlUXWAiahWLoKhBYxLzpiwyyR_9JFvUzhMh38Blr5oFYoO3exzm9k1M8r8GodlJfwKXCa53XFS9bQRrBAhBCDeX_PtMhG0r-D671EXbWH-GPKlp4n_MeOg/VkI5G64oGux3yfjRiSBgg52idXTohkZp/7" target="_blank"&gt;可能会对该行业产生灾难性影响&lt;/a&gt;。对关税价格上涨的恐惧已经促使&lt;a href="https://l