遵循他本周在集团上对所谓的互惠关税征收所谓的互惠关税，它将采用&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/AtwOQdeK8TGYM7JBkmywV6WL6GD0IigM1rSgLTMupiDpGrGKBZeNkLPcn_dLVO-8M54Zu16tndVEAGqecJi0cI-zxo4sPxpLYO7pIt7CQRMAoTMVPtAGtAqlCUJI1o6YleddLrxg0rCRyL9TKZaSkpuXYIwjB1ubI4MTalKiz6huazrEf4gpxGC7nG3GCjoWQW7UkHO6rcyRgWKrFJSNGKrDUSwSesGF9C2ZJnJfYxuoaXQuhag7sVVaeJ56QQI-oHrQ9PB88ZEaeZE2IIUFu2ktExD1rGEnwgGmkfsFzf2fZdVl1uEg92E4rdCohRLpc_7PBd5YKSQGBIJCh8ixz4LTmwLwbBrf7ycdvAhykOZ3rKXK_3CWxYm30Bs/2CQZFdQYL5mj8x4Xea_QBCFPalF0r-6z/7" target="_blank" title="关联"&gt;各种各样的选择&lt;/a&gt;来对美国进行报复。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;商务部长霍华德·卢特尼克（Howard Lutnick）表示，他可以拒绝保证筹码的赠款，因为他推动公司以联邦半导体补贴为准，以&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/lryvYRV5p31h9mcsdXUAD4CR60AQ3QWL-n7rmoB5txhJPr6jsA3lQC3qG5zPdLKLu9-SwuRevoa9zEw9nUwB1D2W31CHcX9yFxzlhC_87xL-SX_SfzkowHBkmVJd5s1pBNx-WAwO0jkdDLF3h15AVJR-uVNfO2qUeCDtIIylBBlvZqm1wCSvilwzmkVLoiLQ9xom8V9JyqojY0eq71tDDLzNC8cc4pMJsBVbebhUJ6hkV2N1yc8FXqHvFbK_MsOpufdwDhk0APSG3mWg5NuqW8HWcx8-YtWhcxOWF58tA3-q8AW-XjFR7aqivfXWMsFXgzv8QrD7vssgSGxFxtuvPRaoFG7N85rsri0an0SJfkWbPaO8P5e0VSXALAM/VinFxKIN2ciBDu6z3tb2Z16JhUq_gzNZ/7" target="_blank" title="关联"&gt;大大扩展其美国项目&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;美国汽车制造商正在&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/1uINg861mjgroYXdyym1TcvtE_bEYDdwtf3P9mZYOOIbOcLk3D-PEn4wtP2TFXuWuSg3PvH9BjlWz3Ze52fN3abXw3rHi_KQmPB5SuRlvWBjQefjsYldi7JR75Wj3HJzh-I932j35TIECAoTeu_mJorZdivmmHQ_kC6LghIYbNHX0kPXSRSx9tOwqxz7B6G1In-_QGfMOkYX0HfeLs4p2Cm1FjaCHiMjywKh1-xVl6q4reeqduYlnsLh6teRSe6ioqGcHTT7NLYVL604fO3sU4o2x5wKgsZJ-MuSYq74OPBcwwjMXa4A665n5SEo32jYcyb03b2BxlKMR6On541NB7TcWWnXTse83H0x8m7_IoGf3GHCIzQYUJmLPyg/pw2Jx0yK41P4nvR37GUa6TqeqSALcklc/7" target="_blank" title="关联"&gt;竭尽全力&lt;/a&gt;将特朗普推向本周将生效的关税，认为税款可能会产生灾难性的影响。福特，通用汽车和斯特兰蒂斯正在游说管理以排除某些汽车组件。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;h2&gt;泡沫恐惧&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;忘记关税，政府支出削减和经济衰退的威胁。对于技术股票的投资者来说，这是对&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/bn_9yB3Y9Q0XIwkDrepvgLzMuijZvlAkmJztNKqEZRYY0uEmvp6e87yr6e9K7DdI-zBfRjo3wxAo7oiDRCtEqM-INqOHjOwiOllAPhQEroeaTBEiz6u3ifR5E-dLC5UpK9eXMD84zItQ9DwGUed_2IB3e6yipVveCW1zXp0o_a9os7lRgGagcg_yT8BkK_4CO6QLdEMZEP4tJP3b9Fg4N6cMT7dT4RaAyqGqRmWkMbnCpeURGaMzrNEXlHt0zw4OSjIoY6iSAqBE-1Toh5nVELpWqoWr_LClub-ZsozDAEdn2gkgUb4L2COqGDKenSHoplXBaZnNtya1fJF0AaDISlkUJE9ebHJN95hNVxW69gQxWjRHhTW3irRKHFs/4m_w3_6Iv5ol6iMafjiMRj01OI4KH5gu/7" target="_blank" title="关联"&gt;AI中泡沫酿造的泡沫&lt;/a&gt;的担忧。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;纳斯达克100指数刚刚发布&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/YXE_nh39lcXgmDQ_X1l22M9cgUCTOpIqis271PNS8Uh9ZG4ijQqEnEV8N6D5tsfdmTGyLd-MAxPpLPN7seq16GZsUNfMkSSttNikSlB6XES8n3s9yuJzHPkzQMkj_0y1fblbwsH26SgOWb7xEnnNPdCjS6ijumw4pz1wNB7K9V_JPkrekSdw7BCNzTGWy9esUwXt82Sc0hoyZbRk17UeR8kB6SF6RS6mMM7tF2vD2dsadbHmeCLnY5c0YmkouulMS7BlhTZkzj4leasahHm4ueoa4akNiHyGybKn1YNTLgUQ4oAbsfw8u_3nEKGvvReIyLwXNWaRooIowqdlkMQiDy8qwOu3A6DjFwzqMmcNDCchoTBqJTZgly_q3o0/O2GHhpe0xLEm-sahKxnEAXILpX1eTWgw/7" target="_blank" title="关联"&gt;了&lt;/a&gt;将近三年来最大的季度下降，下降了8.3 &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/UTMvE3Rrd1bkmhC-w6h3EEYeJJPQ7vxdOGLN3LLwqTDQwY3I961QWvcQaIVTAKid0wV17NlfBW6mF0x4LLFQXUcFpzgIrujybQrR8ddedYdvW83jmmGO8lKAj25waG_BO_L0i21MydMpEcNbUCAUoDji4usPbg2NIGVM38lGcX1BnAr-jxHqW-dm37UrY1Swi5kK16yf4T-vNbWwplEuThqXzR2JPjErzMgubal0D5UIDyMNpISqJIn9dtQEK-7b9xXUflMymTJsAPtKsb94DZRw99hTQPY0NIh0TnUzNryN2wum9DsbNF-P80rp4K7GxxDAwg2lV8qMeAL17__tbT6N4YDZ4n5Z8_4ALrXHN9CJnRTE4YqFXA2yLqo/RCWJCWhdPWMgPDX_OLU9WSu-zyUeKU79/7" target="_blank" title="关联"&gt;％&lt;/a&gt; 。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ih7CAXeJaZug/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ih7CAXeJaZug/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" style="display: block; width: 530px; margin: auto;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;直到最近才成为市场最大的驱动因素的股票中，损失仍在堆积。芯片制造商Nvidia从一月份的山峰开始就看到其股份跌幅为28％。 Microsoft，Amazon.com，Alphabet和Meta都从自己的记录中下降了20％或更多。&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;波士顿合作伙伴全球市场研究总监迈克尔·穆兰尼（Michael Mullaney）表示：“关于AI的问题总体上增加了不确定性，以及它们以完美或接近它的定价的时候。” “对于那些对利润造成利润的人来说，这使他们成为非常明显的地方。”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;在IPO市场上，令人沮丧的是，云层的提供商Coreweave上周备受期待的首次亮相是愚蠢的。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;对于Bokeh Capital Partners的首席投资官Kim Forrest来说，整个情况表明，紧张的投资者在人工智能支出方面的放缓如何变得如何。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;福雷斯特谈到Coreweave首次亮相时说：“这将是去年6月的狂热。” “所有这些加起来，追逐计算中心的需求太少。” - &lt;em&gt;&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/CvRfz2u3wZgei74EYaArdvP0uIdBKNkWCDDjBpgvcPBnWHNCQqJC6wvit9m-tzg8VnCCaZdQgxGLgETSUk68C-tWELNzgIpufu8J3at2a_id4O-SFOWfasUgg4N6mNpvi0ElTpdpFOMNHuEkbFTpunNstg9R9C-OSvBLiHaMoakK5FLmFMAhk5XYhaFekS25Jaor1X-0HDw3DPrqv6vtsnzgU-Rdp2b2XdVQDxjG7SMDUIP0jD_EvDjzKWs2M-7ie_j-0T0FC4U060zBuj6ZInOr-8mGIIvExVC_j5IpulCZ5joriKEukmut-PY6Rn456ezd33m__H4QXmpT4RhPf8qZVhTYcM1lSaZXylAFEU_3dya9mZsTvua2mLM/D4ICCf7maBs8LMFQU28BbdCV3JV52OSO/7" target="_blank" title="关联"&gt;Jeran Wittenstein&lt;/a&gt;和&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/L_n7QBYAHsvmh6fwRpeb9mgoXPVNC1oNzYfsmliBJAjXEmhlSrlmVx5kqjKhestReyt6MwkbjC3QtufVuKZkFYNFYhOEg_EiiGKV70CVmxkLzF3nU1xGkyViZDuHxbexxbcRkmp_cVZwH7XIf0UyodjASy9SAwbuZlOS0CLW6mgmolX4ynKd23kgcVKsGAY3z0lo8qeIj1z2jvxY6QdvoGZbg53HaUMasnxn7WXoQHUZNr-1L-rCdbghS0uIOmjxi3FrzdET7bOOzkKmizH-iD9hj49-CJGa2jICx_V_9dtx2eVbKrm0DdnVA-N9DoQVPTFyQ5D4f0Bv-o6SDXmIdxrFjr3sn-Mkl9uJ9tDxrHfaQYLs902k6cVe3m4/RV_ZYLvKeVdgXvghfiqFDoByKiICfNrN/7" target="_blank" title="关联"&gt;Ryan Vlastelica&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/em&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;table align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="auto"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td align="center" colspan="2" style="padding: 0 0px;" valign="top"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/0FWQtrWFuYeqz-jbWlKrUc0MKp2sKMi9Vcka0feX0bLnCUJjWghB8fOUc07JSGmJETeVRaIW3jM_BmLd4KQXL1e0fbt3wA2Coxn_aitNBWWrCq_QU09hsbx9vAYygBuaqfky_II6SpwSKMduK7_hmc1kxw3A6V522BLKoq3LHcbsIkFYvJVq0uYvVnLV5k2u7a6DPaV7WMNKXc25Y-txrw9qDM-GQ0AuKxwC8Flz9A_kix1JK0wnYB0HEh4QCvjLujY5EClCtZktJ3SVU2MpAnzwgUmlvRKWyMi2rROoliDNs4TOKO0LI6JhazSuGxOZA3luCp_KtjKP6p6_pnB3iNBQvI5u3oZqIqxcgHpDK4PM2dcjr8TofVOo0B0Pp0PYR-bIpr0aUn7bICwdOqIFvCXJDVFidCpbp3Y3TLMH-aLJo40GzRk2VmUbgOTNNvcw0Ml__Ed8SA75QkZFqRO9aJjl6KapZO7pBgW8t_H_jXj21KEJb7HmXsQ27vVysyn35O7vX7-wUZXhdHAI4dQdXgQPzPfRzh4rqYZXtCi4djU4zRiW_rTCnHxnTX0OGqpIuBFMfEi5GzBJox9kgXF5SvU-07oRtcKA06Pbdl8BN5E17xGZ/Cn4RtkwMs3I4ymxDsobtG_dbXtn8558g/7" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" class="lihide" src="https://sli.bloomberg.com/imp?s=1099824&amp;amp;stpe=default&amp;amp;li_coord=desktop&amp;amp;collapse_width=550&amp;amp;li=13081364&amp;amp;m=d42b0cd27465a66be4227a135cb7a14e&amp;amp;p=0401202