 16px; line-height: 24px;" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;ul style="padding-left: 10px; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;保守派媒体&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;Newsmax&lt;/strong&gt;的股票在上市交易中上涨了26％，在昨天的首次亮相会议上飙升了&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/TTuj935h-RaLz-iBEowsXw9_s0sjBmToj1k-q2GmHnTvtslUREGHRTh0cpIAksAtjZh4ScF6plsyFoHma_XLyyN0pFIQdR8YdffzBM_0hmmO5XYtUPJgxZhdgJ3C6pN_uBsCZFI_sekAOKzuS2MWizyWLocmDfAs-Nlp71qDJ4Uavh3X7sPussVLdoo9ZqjToThfzH-sxc_U69sXHtXdrjsfvyN5KfJNAy4AG7Kv91mfFlNmBJ_jW98803cM12xTDKIgwS-4BTpOULBa0C5y0hUEZluJsxDqqEZaUgWZquZ4HIk2-vqX7FhfHCKxpjYLp2IGsrBhXul1jwYKXhw8xtDR24A2XyBsPop4IoRujoGjXBenRqUs96Nmmyc/52bcTTlOuafNhRBCZQcR0VhZD6XVd_vw/7" target="_blank"&gt;735％，&lt;/a&gt;这使该股有望扩大增长。该公司&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/QdznsfES7rWDmQpLbEGxHJAHYneswy5hd3oPeHRHTy_wTMGQYPcJPwKiAxqZ1OPHjrbvwCek_tX29HP-CwaifdM_0zcsIpCMRS3wQt1g_cYfBhguq76swYqTAqscxG5TZl_kwzgStkHwDqNYlnk0mhAnva1Ea1pQdgA2o0r6VvoA-rwS_Y2uk3UbKa6jtZXjJqeqJZWvcwBw48j9hzT7CCZyTkSV0cpLSJc5XF_OzR9ifJlCBHOj9AmfU7O5UGjpc301wFIgmcMhMX-yzofHv3Ce1uR8WBmbXKpUJ50NebqhN96piYn7OEG_J9Yzr40lntQ-DJ5JlS95rIYZyYTbDCcW_VVnviBBnHQ98Zx3x_HEvAGk1PM_vBUR3D4/92lOJnchzgOyFSoTJEcvQ2X3qNlDfBoZ/7" target="_blank"&gt;筹集了&lt;/a&gt;7500万美元的IPO。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;约翰逊和约翰逊&lt;/strong&gt;下跌2.7％。一名联邦法官&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/LOhRZFZ_rEPRUEklTdRza6oVi4MUodD-akL6P9FEkYPA4pkJdFPVN-IRo7qgypdIdGBoPa0_OjVAXTYo4juBoZYJ9shGjV-8jUK_PNlSxe22mcp7ul2o1TnRVm0IdzYMEw8hUp9kFdfdTa3DkpTuY4p9gQbqerwSEbrUWLLPR5gxgLECd4GSVgd-8T3fNdtrP6WNE5J9feDNNozKL831K3JAFbm1pN9r8a2TpOZlTXEAlTgjRPnkOEXB8ZIJVPZHEW9ZjPmqQCaK0n0i2xDwbHvfZtgwALWZro4IUgNtoQ7azJuC-klr3SxC5w-wIOZgVRD9eI51fgbvtw-_5auFFJxNyandL1OsOngMxBgyU0BcJWkNkMDMREXIP5I/a8f1q