"font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;标准普尔500标准普尔（S＆P 500）在该季度结束了4.6％，这是&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/ljPY0uk9-f9L2UXgi09DaPjYP7XlCH2XIXiXzTkXmMMCjf7r11nTW_AZEBnmd0UUE_VfH7rsMGczmOiw673Yklh7GUMArns-qVqHpK1xMgUFj9ZuPvsU7T5J5JKscWU4O7sKyeijdI1M5OhDOYg8fcy1iXwpa2Z3yCB-X75P0is9L2PsEqdY0ubhixEpyVgPUk9Mbhaezo5oy5RrTC1uOlZSu7c4GnNd8eG_2a13zu2gLoArLpPK5N4qXM8mpyOmpmy1KCr_R5FwC9LPJ0OU8Y1SFt2cKbcCKpSxlPHk56U1hkpBbC28GGNh1rWMSli8se3fQgevTGwyUr0ZAQWVllEAb_34yswuxXk2a3GlxCTb4btZPSIR0e4-h4XxwftFEaVcQl9ZMCUOsDKMvXNSI64jFqGPrpdsyz18cepN9NdThhz7tWvWg63H7DPX3lJtp7PkX8BIebDEHzD0qRqtkloC0sbcio8gtHqsgnUFMhOh9tieVbssCJC2ZrFnkjpF9nNF_99Rv2KNVoiku_k4KyjIE_GFFznHlGmaEt6Oiw/pNDBO8G_1qDs4rLZ-kGjQu_s9pDPMIok/7" target="_blank"&gt;三年&lt;/a&gt;来最差的表现。纳斯达克100号&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/pHIEpYEqUrfblc53nKrebC7zjd89sQtaESWv40JEU6JAInSPoB77Th4ztfXWSmBwNZOnCu_cADb8cVAx5t8tXs4FB--MIM2s_UWIgMCTBzbYE_rt0vWTbD8OYnqUSbwm5tdTFI-hd8mpD7ms8fmIUugdBUhWP5y2HkHqzwE2Aq0qzAM8qnWeOujtlAX07NuTamggJmbVgl-J92PT99dbf43TyJuxOJz7nTsG87HKrOoy4l06q8peHZQMEUzYZnA9_lErScypVuAjwI7xwJV5lUaKLS5MML55VicWvH8HG9Vynh8L_sWeAOanHGaSAdU52QBm4MkI4jLeHAI9qw5-2Wx383pWqxZFWeWZ2ti36pztqaNWN6w1eqhDWw/pLMDnhz_LYZ4_OJ1MJVdta9RecCd9n-a/7" target="_blank"&gt;在近三年内发布了最糟糕的季度&lt;/a&gt;，下跌了8.3％，因为上周有两次警告使人们对流入数据中心基础设施的数千亿美元可能的回调感到焦虑。对于美国而言，美元的情况变得更糟， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/sK1LZaDhUxtQUUEZiSPVoY1GBk_02ip7grzZkEcG-T3a9684-uu5tpRiY-1wdfKCphnWcCwqYksmeJUSv3ipz_4ItikQorsqrKAH3wUJuDqez05b_rUZKdfz1poaxbl3wIhcRHqR6YFaW63fFFG9VqaImP3A1k1cnDdGAjOnItzKJjH2AVMqHkpHcy1ARIH1CVJ1wwZg8w3IfQhcX8ZV7Z1Vg7MIjcQATMz0dCuGJ3gBHdIX0FHu57zqnRitp1RDEhsCzjbjgWMcpmNvtJptW6wlymLv64T13eC96ss9w8fReZa7UFZh868CCIQrBpM_JEg5fc9CDLFMEFAf8r41lFyaq9dSVVQU0-1AfW0ywgwWvSrZ16vqV_isFA/IIWdA92-60COFF2n9TU23QIGrTOwhGSj/7" target="_blank"&gt;美元并没有正常表现&lt;/a&gt;，这引起了&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/BEcCdIVHmMhxcePo9AHJ-eu0a67T7WCKzubN9dzxEH7jMlulnhOWSAyXiPljIYdPlhUiiy_nFSoDo-jwBr6XRbMEC